videos.description: Duke's Daniel Jones has his pass deflected and then intercepted by Justin Strnad.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Strnad picks off Jones

videos.description: John Wolford hits Tabari Hines on a slant route for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wolford finds Hines for Wake Forest TD

videos.description: John Wolford has all day to throw and delivers a 43-yard touchdown pass to Alex Bachman.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Bachman takes pass 43 yards for TD

videos.description: Daniel Jones throws an 18-yard touchdown pass to Daniel Helm, Duke's first touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Jones hits wide open Helm for TD

videos.description: After nearly catching his own pass, Daniel Jones' pass pinballs around and is eventually intercepted by Wake Forest's Demetrius Kemp.
videos.headline: Jones throws INT after crazy bounces

videos.description: Mark Gilbert out muscles Chuck Wade and comes down with an interception for Duke.
videos.headline: Gilbert fights for INT

videos.description: Wake Forest's Amari Henderson elevates to intercept the Daniel Jones pass.
videos.headline: Henderson makes leaping INT

videos.description: Daniel Jones finds Noah Gray in the flat who reaches the end zone backwards for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Duke's Gray backs into end zone for TD

videos.description: Daniel Jones' 1-yard touchdown run puts the Blue Devils up 24-23.
videos.headline: Jones gives Duke the lead

videos.description: Brittain Brown reaches the ball across the goal line for a touchdown that puts Duke up 31-23.
videos.headline: Brown extends Duke's lead
